						<summary>

						<p>This record could be assigned to Rājarāja III on account of the high regnal year. Registers a gift of golden diadem weighing 20 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> and one <hi rend="italic">mañjāḍi</hi> by an individual Aḻiyātiraṉ Viḍaiyiṉ-mēlvaruvāṉ belonging to a village in Paḍuvūr-nāḍu of Maṇayiṟ-kōṭṭam. The gold had been equated to madirāntakaṉ māḍai and Īḻakkāsu.</p>						

						</summary>
